<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1486 Agunēṁṭi krōdhana
<lb n="2" break="no"/>saṁvatsara caitra ba 5 bu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> naṁdapura mahārājya peda
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yallamajīyyaṁgārunnu pinayallammajīyyaṁgā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>runnu tamaku Abhīṣṭārthasiddhigānu siṁhyācalēśvaru
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ni sannidhi nitya māpēranu pratimalu sthāpiṁci nityamuna
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nnu dīpamu Akhaṁḍamugānu veluṁganu dēvuni bhaṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍārānaku dīpakataṁtrānaku saskāni ṭaṁkālu 80 sa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>marppiṁciri Iṁduku dēUḷānanu nityamunnu Aḍḍeṁḍu
<lb n="9"/>camaru peṭṭuvāru Ī dharmamu Ācaṁdrārka
<lb n="10" break="no"/>sthāIgānu samarpiṁciri <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatṛṇāpi kṛtō dharmaḥ
<lb n="11"/>pālanīyyō manīṣibhiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śatṛrēva hi śatṛsyāddharma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied>
<lb n="12"/>śatṛrna kasyacit <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ī dharmaṁ yevvaraṁ khaṁḍi(ta)ṁcu
<lb n="13" break="no"/>vāru kuṁbhīpākādinarakālaṁ baḍuduru Ī
<lb n="14"/>dharmamu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

